{"tid":1874132,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"情緒問題 (理大)","createTime":"2020-02-11T04:33:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T04:33:12.000Z","uid":254946,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"53da2150c8b2e3d8b8b70f8ec710908eefc91cad","tid":1874132,"uid":254946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T04:33:12.000Z","msg":"PolyU應用社會科學系以下有一所輔導中心的，如果大家/識人有需要用到輔導服務，可以考慮。每次只需50大元。<br />\n<br />\n網上申請就可以了： <a href=\"https://www.polyu.edu.hk/pfs/index.php/712859?lang=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.polyu.edu.hk%2Fpfs%2Findex.php%2F712859%3Flang%3Den&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yBphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=7f8d17f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.polyu.edu.hk/pfs/index.php/712859?lang=en</a><br />\n<br />\n服務是由修讀 *諮商與輔導碩士 的受訓輔導員提供，他們都已修讀有關的科目，並由資深導師及教授直接督導*，保證服務專業。<br />\n<br />\n輔導一節約45-50分鐘的面談，在polyu進行。時間可選星期一至五，晚上6:30-8:30或星前六早上10:00-12:00。詳情可參考單張。"}]}